data.description: Huge price improvement, Honey , pack your bags, assumable 3.25 fixed rate interest rate. with an incredibly low Principal and Interest payment of 1169.00...Compare  this home to NEW !,  this freshly painted home POPS as soon as you open the door, 12 ft. ceilings,  grand entry way, plenty of room for your decorating touch, open floor plan with plenty of cabinets and cooking surfaces, its move in ready, carpet has been recently replaced and the garage for all your stuff is 3 car size, its 30 ft. wide. The location also is eligible for a-0 down Rural development loan.
